Consider it as thanks

11
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:18,120
for taking care of me and Bao.

12
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:33,160
Xinxin, I want to tell you the truth.

13
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:35,120
Don't talk to me about any truth.

14
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,980
The truth means nothing to me now.

15
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,480
