16
00:03:43,079 --> 00:03:43,880
Please leave.

17
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:03,720
Xinxin.

18
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:16,480
This is the most precious thing between us.

19
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,720
No matter what happens today,

20
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,720
