21
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:29,200
I need to tell you the truth about what happened three years ago.

22
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:37,960
The story of that night three years ago goes like this.

23
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,000
Dr. Hua, which patient should we operate on first?

24
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,400
The young man's condition is more serious,

25
